'''阿拜亞湖'''（Lake Abaya，阿姆哈拉語︰Abaya Hayk）是[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]][[南方各族州|南方各族州]]的湖泊，位於[[東非大裂谷|東非大裂谷]]，南面是[[查莫湖|查莫湖]]。湖長60公里、闊20公里<ref>''Statistical Abstract of Ethiopia for 1967/68''</ref>，湖泊面積1,162平方公里<ref name="baxter">Baxter, R. M. ''Lake Morphology and Chemistry.'' in Taylor, W.D. and Tudorancea, C., eds. '''Ethiopian Rift Valley Lakes.''' Leiden: Backhuys Publishers, 2002.</ref>，最大深度13.1米，海拔1,285米<ref name="baxter"/>。

阿拜亞湖中央有多個島嶼，每年出產412噸魚穫。<ref>[http://www.fao.org/fi/fcp/en/ETH/body.htm "Information on Fisheries Management in the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fao.org/fi/fcp/en/ETH/body.htm |date=20080228033847 }} (report dated January, 2003)</ref>

